---
---

<header
    id="top"
    class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-16 px-6 md:px-14 pt-[72px] md:pt-[88px] pb-12 md:pb-[48px] md:min-h-[calc(100vh-67px)]"
>
    <div class="max-w-[1100px]">
        <div class="fx ml-3C flex items-center gap-3 text-[14px] font-medium text-accent mb-7">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent block"></span>
            Available for work
        </div>

        <h1 class="fx font-display font-bold text-[clamp(64px,11vw,180px)] leading-[0.88] tracking-[-0.035em] m-0">
            Fernando Montano<span class="text-accent">.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="fx text-[19px] leading-[1.6] text-ink-muted max-w-[460px] mt-[34px]">
            A passionate engineer building high-scalable code and exceptional UX — and pixel-perfect design in between.
        </p>

        <div class="fx flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-[38px]">
            <a href="#work" class="bg-ink text-paper text-[15px] font-medium px-[26px] py-[14px] rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity duration-300">
                Selected work
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="border border-[#cfcabd] text-[15px] font-medium px-[26px] py-[14px] rounded-full hover:border-ink transition-colors duration-300">
                Get in touch
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fx flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2">
        <span class="text-[14px] text-ink-faint">Currently Fullstack Developer @ Willdom</span>
        <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-line min-w-6"></span>
        <a href="https://github.com/montanoo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="navlink text-[14px] font-medium">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fernandojmontano/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="navlink text-[14px] font-medium">LinkedIn</a>
    </div>
</header>
